Coerce an mrgsimsds object to a tbl

Source: R/collect.R
as_tibble.mrgsimsds.Rd

Coerce an mrgsimsds object to a tbl

Usage

# S3 method for class 'mrgsimsds'
as_tibble(x, ...)

# S3 method for class 'mrgsimsds'
collect(x, ...)

# S3 method for class 'mrgsimsds'
as.data.frame(x, row.names = NULL, optional = FALSE, ...)

Arguments

x

an mrgsimsds object.

...

passed to dplyr::as_tibble() or dplyr::collect().

row.names

passed to base::as.data.frame().

optional

passed to base::as.data.frame().

Value

A tbl containing simulated data.

Examples

mod <- house_ds(end = 5)

out <- mrgsim_ds(mod, events = ev(amt = 100))

tibble::as_tibble(out)
